Note from the author



Thank you very much to DimitriTiwatLambda for encouraging me to write this.

Also thanks to YossiLeiner for reviewing the translation.

This started after I translated some Fifthist SCP and tales and these. There were fantastic, but I missed one thing: a more literal approach to stars. And after three or four months I finished this.

Enjoy my second SCP for the second week and the first Fifthist -ES article (Not everything is going to be second.). Although is my second article, is my most upvoted article :)

Hope you like it! I'm eager to read your opinion!!

- morhadow
